Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
defOutPolygonDieArea(25.10)                        defOutPolygonDieArea(25.10)

Name
       defOutPolygonDieArea

Syntax
        defOutPolygonDieArea {0 | 1}

       Type: Integer

       Default: 1

       By  default,  defOut writes out polygon DIEAREA if the design is recti-
       linear. To write out rectangular DIEAERA along with blockages  in  cut-
       out area for a rectilinear design, set this variable to 0.

Related Information
              * defOut

